<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
	<meta charset="euc-kr">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>NICE지키미</title>

	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/ui.common.js"></script>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/rzm/common.css">
	<script type="text/javascript">
		mbHeader = { title: '로그인', prev: true, menu: true };

		$(function () {
			modal.openModal('#modal');
		});
	</script>
</head>

<body>
	<div id="wrap">
		<div id="skipNavi"> 
			<a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a> 
		</div>
		<!-- header -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
		<!--// header -->

		<!-- container -->
		<div id="container">
			<div id="content">
				<div class="section">
					<a href="#modal" class="btn base modalOpen">가입정보 갱신요청(휴대폰)</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--// container -->

		<!-- popup -->
		<div class="uiModal full" id="modal">
			<div class="modalWrap">
				<button type="button" class="uiBtn typeModalClose"><span class="hidden">닫기</span></button>
				<div class="modalHeader">
					<h1>가입정보 갱신요청</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="modalContent">
					<div class="inner">
						<!-- content -->
						<div class="governing">
							<h2 class="governingTitle">
								김신용회원님, 휴대전화번호를 다시 등록해 주세요
							</h2>
						</div>
						<div class="formWrap">
							<div class="formItem">
								<label for="hpnum" class="titItem">휴대전화번호</label>
								<div class="intBtnType">
									<input type="tel" id="hpnum" placeholder="- 없이 숫자만 입력">
									<div class="intBtn">
										<button type="button" class="btn base"><span>인증번호 요청</span></button>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="formItem">
								<label for="lognum" class="titItem">인증번호 입력</label>
								<div class="intBtnType">
									<input type="tel" id="lognum" maxlength="6" placeholder="숫자 6자리 입력">
									<div class="intBtn">
										<button type="button" class="btn base"><span>확인</span></button>
									</div>
								</div>
								<p class="guideTxt">인증번호 요청은 1일 3회까지만 가능합니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="uiAcco infoTip">
							<div class="uiAccoHeader">
								<button type="button" class="uiBtn">
									<span class="accoTitle">꼭 알아두세요!</span><span class="hidden">펼치기</span>
								</button>
							</div>
							<div class="uiAccoContent">
								<ul class="listDot">
									<li>회원님이 기존에 등록한 휴대전화번호가 다른 계정과 중복되니, 다시 등록해 주시기 바랍니다.</li>
									<li>[인증번호 요청]을 눌러 휴대전화로 받은 인증번호 입력 후 [확인]을 누르면 휴대전화번호가 등록됩니다.</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
						<!--// content -->
					</div>
					<div class="modalBottom">
						<div class="btns">
							<button type="button" class="btn second"><span>나중에</span></button>
							<button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>갱신완료</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--// popup -->

		<!-- footer -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/footer.js"></script>
		<!--// footer -->
	</div>
</body>

</html>